description:
&lt;p&gt;Bisley Lodge provides a unique package of care and support 24hours a day and 365 days a year, for some of the most vulnerable Young people age 17 - 24 in our care system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our aim here at Bisley Lodge is to ensure that the Young people we invest in have the best residential experience in a homely environment. Care here is individually tailored and we aim to make the experience as positive and beneficial as possible. We work hard to meet individual needs and truly invest in our Young people’s future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for the supervision of young people who display a range of emotional, behavioural, psychological and other mental health problems in particular self -injury. You will assist young people with the devolpment of their education and also with the development of their life skills. &lt;/p&gt;
